The '''1894 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their fourth ever season of organized football. The Keydets held a 6-0 record, their first undefeated season in team history.<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
